ift\"'`\n- `rg -n \"WakeAlarm|WakeRun|WakeStrictness|WakeMission\" apps/waketask-iphone/Packages apps/waketask-iphone/SwiftAIBoilerplatePro -g '\"'*.swift'\"'`\n- `sed -n '\"'1,240p' apps/waketask-iphone/Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/Resources/en.lproj/Localizable.strings\"'`\n- `sed -n '\"'1,260p' apps/waketask-iphone/scripts/qa/appium-exploratory-tapper.sh\"'`\n- `sed -n '\"'1,220p' apps/waketask-iphone/SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/AppShell/AppRootView.swift\"'`\n- `sed -n '\"'1,260p' apps/waketask-iphone/Packages/Core/Sources/Core/WakeTask/WakeTaskModels.swift\"'`\n- `sed -n '\"'1,260p' apps/waketask-iphone/SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/Previews/PreviewComposition.swift\"'`\n- `sed -n '\"'1,320p' apps/waketask-iphone/SwiftAIBoilerplatePro/Previews/PreviewMocks.swift\"'`\n- `sed -n '\"'1,260p' apps/waketask-iphone/Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/Resources/es.lproj/Localizable.strings\"'`\n- `cat <<'\"'EOF' >> apps/waketask-iphone/Packages/Localization/Sources/Localization/Resources/es.lproj/Localizable.strings ... EOF\"'`\n- `rg -n \"bodySemibold|statusError|wakeFlowViewModel|L10n.Wake|wakeAddAlarmButton|wakeAlarmCell\" apps/waketask-iphone -g '\"'*.swift'\"'`\n- `cd apps/waketask-iphone && xcodebuild -list -project SwiftAIBoilerplatePro.xcodeproj | head -n 80`\n- `git -C /home/daytona/workspace diff --name-only`\n- `git -C /home/daytona/workspace status --short apps/waketask-iphone | sed -n '\"'1,120p'\"'`\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- Implemented real WakeTask interface flow (alarm list, new alarm creation, strictness selection, start run, mission completion, wake-check, first-task completion, dismiss) in `WakeDashboardView` using existing `WakeFlowViewModel` and AppShell navigation.\n- Preserved existing app shell and navigation structure; integrated wake interface through `MainTabView` and `AppRootView` with CompositionRoot factory usage.\n- Used DesignSystem tokens/components in the new interface (colors, typography, spacing).\n- Localized all newly u